H-6PjFyvpKg.keywords: 3ds mario eminem furby flare ps3 mkds wii tutorial games code mkwii lol ctww psp darkflare pinky play find save kart hack lets deaththeglaceon yourself flashcart cfw iso rom nintendo gaming eazy ps4 amiibo ps2 sony ps1 gamepad ctgpr mk7 nand spider3ds gateway xd mk8 loloadcode3DS How To Get Private Headers Using Powersaves 3DSIn this video, I'll be showing you how to get private headers from your game cartridges using Powersaves 3DS. It's pretty simple if you have all the required materials. Once you find the headers, they can be used with Gateway and Sky3DS to avoid bans from online play. Nintendo started cracking down on piracy, but we beat them again P WHAT YOU'LL NEED 1 Powersaves 3DS or Powersaves 3DS Pro 2 Game cartridge to get the header from 3 Computer with HxD Hex editor & Powersaves 3DS software. TUTORIAL This is a noob friendly tutorial, step by step. Original tutorial by LameNobody GBAtemp. PreSetup Download HxD PreSetup Download & install the Powersaves 3DS software. 1 Put your game cartridge into your Powersaves 3DS. 2 Plug the Powersaves 3DS hardware into one of the USB ports on your computer. 3 Go to CUsersUSERNAMEPowersaves3DS and move all the '.bin' files to another location You must move them, not simply copy. 4 Make a backup on the Powersaves software. Name it something easily recognizable, but unique, because you'll have to find it later in a hex editor. 5 Close Powersaves 3DS software. 6 Open Powersaves 3DS software Don't ignore these steps. 7 Minimize the Powersaves 3DS window. 8 Open HxD Hex Editor. 9 At the toolbar at the top, go to "Extras  Open RAM..." and choose the "Powersaves3DS.exe" application. 10 Press 'CTRL  F' on your keyboard 11 Type the name of your backup For example, mine was called 'HeaderFile' 12 Look for '00 00 00 88' in the hex values. 13 Everything after that until 'FF FF FF FF' is your private header! 14 Copy the bytes in between '00 00 00 88' and 'FF FF FF FF' and save them to a .txt file. 15 Done! You've successfully found your game cartridge's private header. DOWNLOADS HxD Powersaves 3DS software Thanks for watching! I hope this helped. Qj2rVeyl-e8.keywords: adapter car charger power supply USBUniversal Power AdapterUniversal Power AdapterEvery day we have to deal with a large number of portable devices, MP3 players, communicators, smart phones, Bluetooth headsets and other devices. As you know, any device if it operates on battery must be recharged. But hardly anyone would like to carry a bunch of charging devices with him. Therefore, universal power adapters are very popular. This adapter allows you to save space, since it can replace multiple chargers. This model is an adapter that is designed for those who has to carry a set of all possible devices during a day. You can charge multiple devices with it MP3 players, communicators, smart phones, Bluetooth headsets and others, where USB charging is allowed. The model we describe has a small size and it is rather handy. The adapter is very simple to use just plug it into the car cigarette lighter. Red LED lights up, it means that the adapter is on. Now you can connect the device you want to charge through the USB port. Input voltage 1224V. Output voltage 5V. When the battery is full simply remove the adapter from the cigarette lighter, switchingoff device. That's all simple and easy.
